<item>
            <title>[LUCENE-2636] Create ChainingCollector</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-2636</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                        <description>&lt;p&gt;ChainingCollector allows chaining a bunch of Collectors, w/o them needing to know or care about each other, and be passed into Lucene&apos;s search API, since it is a Collector on its own. It is a convenient, yet useful, class. Will post a patch w/ it shortly.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
